{"tid":765340,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺志矮好撚酸？","createTime":"2018-08-02T16:11:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-03T14:37:41.000Z","uid":5652,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9c5ca9d1178f04665cf7c84d94dfa930f0906bae","tid":765340,"uid":5652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T16:11:48.000Z","msg":"成日訪問佢都講到出晒面好想做 又話tvb未搵佢做港姐主持未開始傾咁<br />\n實情係佢啲港姐去西貢搞都唔知 要靠記者先知 根本一早飛甩左佢冇打算搵佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後就口出狂言酸到爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果tvb真係封殺佢真係唔知佢點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n好彩都仲有個仔係新晉導演幾叻仔養下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6617e0a979a7a5a395010a51143e05084355291","tid":765340,"uid":20816,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T16:17:46.000Z","msg":"貪污錢養大<br />\n唔知點解咁多人崇拜佢"},{"pid":"59fd3b0dd725380b4fab4fe948a81db2347dae5a","tid":765340,"uid":5652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6617e0a979a7a5a395010a51143e05084355291","tid":765340,"uid":20816,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T16:17:46.000Z","msg":"貪污錢養大<br />\n唔知點解咁多人崇拜佢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T16:45:00.000Z","msg":"小心啲講野"},{"pid":"6d183fc9d63f1742809ab8210d36da29db14cacf","tid":765340,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59fd3b0dd725380b4fab4fe948a81db2347dae5a","tid":765340,"uid":5652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6617e0a979a7a5a395010a51143e05084355291","tid":765340,"uid":20816,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T16:17:46.000Z","msg":"貪污錢養大<br />\n唔知點解咁多人崇拜佢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T16:45:00.000Z","msg":"小心啲講野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T16:56:27.000Z","msg":"曾啟榮於1930年代加入廣州警察，與香港著名藝人譚詠麟之父譚江柏為廣州交通督察同事，也是足球隊隊友，所以兩家屬世交，交情匪淺。<br />\n<br />\n1940年加入香港警隊。逐步升任香港總警長，是呂樂的屬下。<br />\n<br />\n1975年，曾啟榮被廉政公署拘捕及指控串謀貪污，其名下5座物業遭到凍結。曾啟榮於1976年4月，律政司申請覆核刑期時，潛逃至與香港沒有罪犯引渡協議的台灣，從此被永久通緝及未再返回香港，長居台北市民生社區。<br />\n<br />\n2006年，曾啟榮90大壽時，曾家一連2日為其在台北大擺筵席，大批香港、台灣明星及前同僚均到台灣為其祝壽。<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/曾啟榮\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E6%9B%BE%E5%95%9F%E6%A6%AE&d=ArrcyyGxfM2i%2FmCk0U9pVMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=4c29ed8b\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/曾啟榮</a>"},{"pid":"0ce901a8e5723ac4705ccdd2209232a3dddf4d06","tid":765340,"uid":5652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T01:49:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78518513545d95a8b7389cc3023da6fdd20a820f","tid":765340,"uid":5652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T14:37:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}